:Class TimerSimple : MiPageSample
⍝ Control:: _DC.Timer
⍝ Description:: Signal timed events to the server

    ∇ Compose
      :Access public 
      Add _.h4'Timer Sample - will append timestamp every 2 seconds (5 times)'
      Add _.Timer 2000
      COUNTER←0 ⋄ LIMIT←5
      'output'Add _.div
      On'tick' 'cb'
    ∇

    ∇ r←cb
      :Access public
      COUNTER+←1
      r←(COUNTER≤LIMIT)/'#output'Append'<br/>Now the time is: ',⍕3↓⎕TS
    ∇

:EndClass